---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    category: "身体状况",
    categoryEn: "Physical Condition",
    questions: [
      {
        q: "没有高原经验可以参加吗？",
        qEn: "Can I join without high-altitude experience?",
        a: "可以。我们的行程会安排2-3天在拉萨（3650米）适应海拔。但建议出发前咨询医生，确认身体状况适合高原活动。严重心肺疾病、高血压患者不建议参加。初次上高原者，建议提前1-2周开始服用红景天。",
        aEn: "Yes. Our itinerary includes 2-3 days in Lhasa (3,650m) for acclimatization. However, please consult your doctor before departure to confirm you are fit for high-altitude activities. Those with severe heart/lung conditions or hypertension are not advised to join. First-timers should start taking Rhodiola 1-2 weeks in advance."
      },
      {
        q: "高原反应严重怎么办？",
        qEn: "What if I get severe altitude sickness?",
        a: "团队配备氧气罐和常用药品。如遇严重高反，向导会立即安排下撤至低海拔地区，必要时使用卫星电话呼叫救援。所有路线均规划了下撤点，确保安全。轻度高反（头痛、恶心）可通过吸氧和休息缓解。",
        aEn: "The team carries oxygen tanks and common medications. For severe altitude sickness, the guide will immediately arrange descent to lower altitude and use a satellite phone to call for rescue if necessary. All routes have planned evacuation points for safety. Mild symptoms (headache, nausea) can be relieved with oxygen and rest."
      },
      {
        q: "需要带什么药品？",
        qEn: "What medications should I bring?",
        a: "建议携带：红景天（提前1周开始服用）、高原安、葡萄糖、感冒药、肠胃药、创可贴。团队也会准备常用药品和氧气。如有特殊疾病，请提前告知并携带个人常用药。",
        aEn: "Recommended: Rhodiola (start 1 week before), Gaoyuan An, glucose, cold medicine, stomach medicine, band-aids. The team also prepares common medications and oxygen. If you have special conditions, please inform us in advance and bring your personal medications."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    category: "装备准备",
    categoryEn: "Gear & Equipment",
    questions: [
      {
        q: "睡袋可以租借吗？",
        qEn: "Can I rent a sleeping bag?",
        a: "可以。我们提供羽绒睡袋租借服务（¥100/全程），但建议使用自己的睡袋更卫生舒适。如需租借请提前告知。",
        aEn: "Yes. We offer down sleeping bag rental (¥100 for the whole trip), but using your own is more hygienic and comfortable. Please let us know in advance if you need to rent."
      },
      {
        q: "登山杖需要自带吗？",
        qEn: "Do I need to bring trekking poles?",
        a: "建议自带，选择双杖可大大节省体力。如不方便携带，我们也提供租借服务（¥50/全程）。",
        aEn: "We recommend bringing your own; using two poles can greatly save energy. If inconvenient to carry, we also offer rental service (¥50 for the whole trip)."
      },
      {
        q: "穿什么衣服合适？",
        qEn: "What clothes should I wear?",
        a: "采用三层穿衣法：内层排汗（速干衣）、中层保暖（抓绒/羽绒）、外层防风防水（冲锋衣）。颜色建议选择鲜艳色彩，拍照好看且便于识别。",
        aEn: "Use the three-layer system: base layer for moisture-wicking (quick-dry), mid layer for warmth (fleece/down), outer layer for wind/water protection (hard shell). Bright colors are recommended for better photos and visibility."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    category: "转山过程",
    categoryEn: "During the Kora",
    questions: [
      {
        q: "转山一定要走三天吗？",
        qEn: "Does the kora have to take three days?",
        a: "标准行程是3天2夜。体力好的 pilgrim 可以选择2天完成（第一天到止热寺，第二天翻垭口后直接回塔尔钦）。也可以雇佣背夫或马匹协助。对于初次朝圣者，建议按3天标准行程，给身体充分的适应时间。",
        aEn: "The standard itinerary is 3 days and 2 nights. Fit pilgrims can complete it in 2 days (Day 1 to Drirapuk, Day 2 cross Dolma La and return to Darchen). Porters or horses can also be hired. For first-time pilgrims, we recommend the standard 3-day schedule to allow adequate acclimatization."
      },
      {
        q: "途中住宿条件如何？",
        qEn: "What are the accommodation conditions along the way?",
        a: "塔尔钦有酒店标间；止热寺和尊最普寺是板房或帐篷通铺，条件简陋但干净，有被子提供。尊享团提供羽绒睡袋和充气垫。建议对住宿条件有合理预期——转山不是度假，而是朝圣。",
        aEn: "Darchen has hotel rooms; Drirapuk and Zutulpuk are simple wooden houses or tent dormitories, basic but clean, with blankets provided. Premium groups get down sleeping bags and inflatable mats. Please have realistic expectations—this is a pilgrimage, not a vacation."
      },
      {
        q: "途中吃什么？",
        qEn: "What is there to eat along the way?",
        a: "塔尔钦有餐厅；转山途中检查站有简单补给（泡面、饼干、开水）。建议自备高能量零食（巧克力、坚果、能量棒）。团队提供早晚餐。注意：高原上食欲会下降，建议少食多餐。",
        aEn: "Darchen has restaurants; checkpoints along the kora offer simple supplies (instant noodles, biscuits, hot water). Bring high-energy snacks (chocolate, nuts, energy bars). The team provides breakfast and dinner. Note: appetite decreases at high altitude, so eat small meals frequently."
      },
      {
        q: "手机有信号吗？",
        qEn: "Is there mobile signal?",
        a: "塔尔钦、止热寺有4G信号；翻垭口途中信号不稳定；部分路段无信号。团队配备对讲机和卫星电话（紧急使用）。建议提前告知家人行程，以免他们担心。",
        aEn: "4G signal is available in Darchen and Drirapuk; signal is unstable while crossing Dolma La; some sections have no signal. The team carries walkie-talkies and a satellite phone (for emergencies). Please inform your family of the itinerary in advance so they won't worry."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    category: "证件手续",
    categoryEn: "Permits & Documents",
    questions: [
      {
        q: "需要什么证件？",
        qEn: "What documents do I need?",
        a: "中国大陆公民：身份证 + 边防证（注明阿里地区）；港澳台同胞：回乡证/台胞证 + 边防证；外籍人士：护照 + 进藏函（需提前通过旅行社办理）。",
        aEn: "Mainland Chinese: ID card + border permit (specifying Ngari region). HK/Macau/Taiwan compatriots: Home Return Permit/Taiwan Compatriot Permit + border permit. Foreign nationals: passport + Tibet Travel Permit (must be arranged through a travel agency in advance)."
      },
      {
        q: "边防证怎么办理？",
        qEn: "How do I apply for the border permit?",
        a: "两种方式：1）在户籍所在地公安局办理（免费，建议提前1周）；2）在拉萨办理（我们可协助，需提前1天）。",
        aEn: "Two ways: 1) Apply at the Public Security Bureau in your household registration city (free, apply 1 week in advance); 2) Apply in Lhasa (we can assist, need 1 day notice)."
      }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title="常见问题 - 冈仁波齐朝圣之旅" description="冈仁波齐朝圣常见问题解答：涵盖身体状况、高原反应、装备准备、转山过程、住宿条件、证件手续等全方位攻略。">
  <!-- Hero: Photo on top, content below -->
  <section class="relative bg-kailash-dark">
    <!-- Full-width photo -->
    <div class="relative w-full h-[45vh] lg:h-[55vh]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/kailash-birds.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-transparent to-kailash-dark"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content below photo -->
    <div class="relative -mt-20 z-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <span data-lang-content="zh">常见问题</span>
          <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">FAQ</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/60 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <span data-lang-content="zh">关于行程、装备、高原反应的一切，这里都有答案</span>
          <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Everything about itinerary, gear, and altitude sickness — answered here</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      {faqs.map((category, idx) => (
        <div class="mb-16 last:mb-0">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 pb-4 border-b-2 border-kailash-gold">
            <span data-lang-content="zh">{category.category}</span>
            <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">{category.categoryEn}</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            {category.questions.map((item, qIdx) => (
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-kailash-dark mb-3 flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-kailash-gold font-bold">Q.</span>
                  <span data-lang-content="zh">{item.q}</span>
                  <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">{item.qEn}</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 pl-7 leading-relaxed">
                  <span data-lang-content="zh">{item.a}</span>
                  <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">{item.aEn}</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Still have questions -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4">
        <span data-lang-content="zh">还有问题？</span>
        <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Still Have Questions?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        <span data-lang-content="zh">没找到您想问的？直接联系我们，我们会尽快回复</span>
        <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Can't find what you're looking for? Contact us and we'll get back to you soon</span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="mailto:kailash2026Lucas@outlook.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-kailash-gold text-kailash-dark px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-accent transition">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">发送邮件</span>
          <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Send Email</span>
        </a>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M8.691 2.188C3.891 2.188 0 5.476 0 9.53c0 2.212 1.17 4.203 3.002 5.55a.59.59 0 0 1 .213.665l-.39 1.48c-.019.07-.048.141-.048.213 0 .163.13.295.29.295a.326.326 0 0 0 .167-.054l1.903-1.114a.864.864 0 0 1 .717-.098 10.16 10.16 0 0 0 2.837.403c.276 0 .543-.027.811-.05-.857-2.578.157-4.972 1.932-6.446 1.703-1.415 3.882-1.98 5.853-1.838-.576-3.583-4.196-6.348-8.596-6.348zM5.785 5.991c.642 0 1.162.529 1.162 1.18a1.17 1.17 0 0 1-1.162 1.178A1.17 1.17 0 0 1 4.623 7.17c0-.651.52-1.18 1.162-1.18zm5.813 0c.642 0 1.162.529 1.162 1.18a1.17 1.17 0 0 1-1.162 1.178 1.17 1.17 0 0 1-1.162-1.178c0-.651.52-1.18 1.162-1.18zm5.34 2.867c-1.797-.052-3.746.512-5.28 1.786-1.72 1.428-2.687 3.72-1.78 6.22.942 2.453 3.666 4.229 6.884 4.229.826 0 1.622-.12 2.361-.336a.722.722 0 0 1 .598.082l1.584.926a.272.272 0 0 0 .14.045c.134 0 .24-.111.24-.247 0-.06-.023-.12-.038-.177l-.327-1.233a.49.49 0 0 1 .177-.554C23.034 18.106 24 16.357 24 14.423c0-3.255-3.01-5.565-6.062-5.565zm-1.951 2.89c.535 0 .969.44.969.982a.976.976 0 0 1-.969.983.976.976 0 0 1-.969-.983c0-.542.434-.982.97-.982zm4.844 0c.535 0 .969.44.969.982a.976.976 0 0 1-.969.983.976.976 0 0 1-.969-.983c0-.542.434-.982.97-.982z"/>
          </svg>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">微信: Kailash2026</span>
          <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">WeChat: Kailash2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQPage Structured Data -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": faqs.flatMap(cat => cat.questions.map(item => ({
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": item.q,
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": item.a
        }
      })))
    })}
  </script>
</Layout>
